title: Python Object Oriented Programming
details: Master object-oriented programming principles in Python. Learn to create and work with classes and objects.

title: Database Management Systems
details: Comprehensive study of database management systems, SQL, and data modeling. Gain expertise in database design.

title: Introduction to C Programming
details: Introduction to the C programming language. Cover syntax, data types, and basic control structures.

title: Algorithms and Data Structures
details: In-depth exploration of algorithms and data structures. Solve complex problems and analyze algorithmic efficiency.

title: Advanced C++ Programming
details: Learn C++ programming with a focus on object-oriented features. Build advanced software applications.

title: Software Engineering Practices
details: Adopt industry-standard software engineering practices, including project management and quality assurance.

title: Problem Solving with Algorithms
details: Develop strong problem-solving skills using algorithmic techniques. Apply algorithms to various domains.

title: Data Structures Fundamentals
details: Explore fundamental data structures such as arrays, linked lists, and trees. Master data organization and manipulation.

title: AWS Cloud Services
details: Get hands-on experience with Amazon Web Services (AWS). Learn to deploy and manage cloud-based applications.
